- "voyage" is a metaphor for the ride in the context of this database;
- "each journey" refers to each unique ride identified by the ride_id in the database.

- "sailing voyages" metaphorically refers to rides taken by users;
- "demographic" refers to groups divided by gender, age, and member duration;
- "time spent in the sea" metaphorically refers to the duration of being a member;
- "wealth they've brought to the harbor" metaphorically refers to the total revenue generated from rides.

